title: Michael Cardinali
text:
Michael Cardinali (born January 14, 1990) is an Italian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
He made his debut on the professional level in the 2006/07 season for the <a href="Serie%20C1">Serie C1</a> team <a href="Giulianova%20Calcio">Giulianova Calcio</a>.
